text: "Satisfied" is a song by American singer Ashley Monroe. It premiered on CMT on March 9, 2006. Satisfied" is a song by American singer Ashley Monroe that premiered on CMT on March 9, 2006. It served as the title track and lead single from her debut album, Satisfied, which was originally intended for release in 2006 but was delayed due to the single's limited commercial success and label issues. The song later appeared on the album when it was finally released as a digital download in 2009. "Satisfied" reached number 43 on the Billboard Hot Country Songs chart in 2006. Category:2006 songs
